<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>

        <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
        <section class="bm-hero">
            <div class="bm-hero-inner">
                <h1 class="bm-hero-title">One System. Multiple Languages.<br>Consistent Service.</h1>
                <p class="bm-hero-subtitle">Automate daily restaurant workflows with AI and IoT—so you can serve more customers, reduce errors, and control costs without hiring more people.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Get started</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== FEATURES ===== -->
        <section class="bm-features" id="features">
            <div class="bm-features-inner">

                <div class="bm-badge">Bhojan Mitra POS</div>

                <div class="rpos-feature-list">

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Multilingual POS &amp; Voice Assistance</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Our system translates languages in real-time, so your staff can use their native tongue. This reduces miscommunication and increases productivity. The result is a more efficient and pleasant work environment for everyone. Now, your staff can focus on providing excellent service.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Faster Training, Minimal Onboarding</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Our onboarding process is now fast and easy, so you can get your staff up to speed quickly. New hires will learn how to use the system in no time. The intuitive design makes it easy to learn. You'll be able to focus on other things.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Consistent Service Across Shifts</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Our system ensures that every shift provides quality service. The system's consistency helps to avoid mistakes. Customers will have a great experience no matter who is working. This will lead to repeat business and positive reviews.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="rpos-feature">
                        <h3 class="rpos-feature-title">Reduced Errors Caused by Misunderstanding</h3>
                        <p class="rpos-feature-desc">Our system helps you avoid errors with simple prompts. The prompts guide you through each step of the process. This reduces the risk of mistakes and ensures accuracy. You can be confident that you're providing the best possible service.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
        <section class="rpos-cta">
            <div class="rpos-cta-inner">
                <h2 class="rpos-cta-title">Want to Know more</h2>
                <p class="rpos-cta-sub">Join the pilot to experience voice ordering, IoT routing, and analytics tailored to your restaurant before our public launch.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bm-btn-primary">Join the program</a>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
